This is a very good evidence to show that the surveillance technology is becoming more and more widespread in current society , especially in our daily healthcare apartments .
Usually these procedures require the patients to suffer quite a lot and need many efforts from the attendants .
By planting this device into their body , we can detect where they are in case some urgent diseases break out .
