It helps to have a good cry and talk things through " ( IMH , 2009 ) .
In conclusion , individuals should not have the final say in revealing their genetic test results for the benefits of the people around them .
With revealing of the results , trust can be generated and relationship between them and their loved ones will become closer .
While some suggest that the use of this technology brings benefits to both country and the world , it in fact not only affects the country 's safety but also the citizens ' privacy in the country .
Thus , due to negative implications that outweigh the benefits of using surveillance technology , it should be banned .
