The idea that reserving retirement fund in advance can ease the aging process is regarded as an efficient and feasible method to the government ( Peterson , 2001 ) .
However , some still think that the younger generation and the government are responsible to deal with the problem coming with aging population .
For example , in a Singaporean middle class family , a young couple usually has two to four children and lives in a governmental or private house with mortgage .
