Singapore has no other natural resources , hence , our most urgent need will be to find a reliable source of sustainable energy .
According to Khandani ( 2005 ) , the design process consists of five main parts : Defining the problem , gathering required information , generating multiple solutions , selecting a solution and testining of the solution .
