The Desert Hawk was design for crush landing ( Staff Sgt .
This was not very popular among the user as it will affect the durability of the machines .
On contrast , the Raven make use of the advance programming to aid landing by making the UAV to experience deep stalling mode ( Army Technology , 2009 ) to greatly reduce speed and impact for landing .
Whenever a change the route during flight , it require some amount of time before the pre-allocated waypoint can be reset .
The Raven was able to switch between two modes of operation such that the second mode allows user to operate the UAV manually ( Army Technology , 2009 ) .
The Raven is now operated by eight military forces around world and still increasing .
While the Desert Hawk is the only user still operating the UAV .
