He invented telephone - a device that allows two remotely located users to communicate by voice between each other ( Mary Bellis , n.d ) .
Similarly , Konrad Zuse has invented the first computer , which satisfies our need for a systematic and efficient method of data management ( Mary Bellis , n.d ) .
