From 1840 to 1949 , Chinese people were suffering from World War II and Chinese civil war .
After these battles and wars , Chinese people finally stepped in to a new era , a peaceful but impoverished era .
Chinese people did not have time to develop their economy and technology .
Therefore , Chinese economy and technology was far behind those developed country .
However , Chinese people did not give up ; Chinese leaders put forward a series of policies .
Moreover , every Chinese people want to contribute to establishing a new China .
That is why Chinese economic situation was much better than before .
For technology aspect , a group of Chinese scientists and engineers scarified their holiday and worked every day and night in order to improve the technology of China .
Therefore , many excellent and designed technological outcomes appeared in that period of time .
But now , there are two factors hamper the design process for innovation .
One is the students are lack of the innovative thinking system .
Learning means to learn and use the knowledge which is taught by teachers .
Thinking means students consider how these theorems derived and how to find the simplest way to solve the problem .
For example , when students are asking teachers questions , they usually would ask I can not solve this problem , why this formula does not work .
However , we want to hear students ask that I have tried a new method to solve this question .
Can you help me check whether is method can use or not .
The main reason for this problem is the Chinese situation .
China has the largest population , and they use the college examination to select the talent people .
Furthermore , the way of testing is give you a lot of question and solve them quickly but not give you one question and solve it in many ways .
There is also limited time for teacher to grade the exam paper .
So if the solution is not the standard solution which is given by ministry of education , the solution is incorrect .
Therefore , students are satisfied in using one way to solve problem .
