Meanwhile , people 's intention to buy brand goods helps deteriorating this problem .
In short , companies may have enough funds for innovation , but that do not mean they can survive the loss of market share just because they are one step behind and let others climb on the top .
With so many things to consider about , those managers do have reasons to hesitate before they risk the future of a company for the unguaranteed profit .
