Firstly , the public has always view that nuclear reactors are unsafe to use as they emit entities which are hazardous to people 's health and the environment .
MSR has a liquid fuel , the reactor has the unique safety advantage that in the event of an accident , the fuel salt is dumped to critically safe , passively cooled storage tanks .
Moreover , molten salts are effectively incompressible ; consequently , a failure of a heat exchanger in the chemical plant will not pressurize the plant .
Also , the public is afraid that the nuclear reactor is misuse for development of nuclear weapon .
This does not concern MSR , as it is able to operate with non-weapon grade fissile fuel which makes it no chance for people to misuse the research to develop nuclear weapons .
Secondly , it has always been a general perception from the public that the cost incurred to build a nuclear reactor is always huge .
This causes not many efforts are being taken to initiate a nuclear reactor project as they believe the project is not feasible .
Another related concern is the amount of cost incurred from the maintainence of the reactor .
However , MSR is known to be among the cheapest nuclear reactor .
Also , MSR will be using thorium as fuel where thorium is so abundant in the world as compare to current technologies which mostly use coals as fuel where coals are expected to last just for another 146years according to Energy Information Administration ( EIA ) .
These show that MSR are economical and should have cleared any doubts regarding further research on MSR as it is a feasible project in the long run as it makes use of resources which are abundant .
If fundings are provided for researches on MSR , there is no doubt that MSR can be fully utilize .
Although MSR generally generate less energy as compared to other nuclear reactors , the lesser space it requires can make up for it .
In conclusion , it is evident that MSR is worth the fundings for the research given the attributes it possess .
If further researches are being done , there is no doubt that MSR will be able to improve its weakness in having higher output as well as further refine on its strong points which is economical and safe to use .
