Looking into every single opportunity to decrease the greenhouse gases emitting into the atmosphere , energy sources may be one of the emphatic points to be revised .
Many of the energy producing sources produce inadmissible air pollutants and greenhouse gases which are very baneful to the environment .
Nuclear power is one of the alternate energy sources that are being considered to arbitrate these problems due to its efficiencies and environmental friendly processes .
Nuclear reactors haven been mistook for a time bomb waiting to be exploded anytime because of the tremendous pressure contained inside .
On the contrary , a bomb is a compact object so the neutrons need not travel far to hit another fissionable atom which made it so powerful .
This is a fact based on the fundamental of physics on how fast fission neutron travels .
